title: Trace of an Operator and of a Matrix

media:group.media:title: Trace of an Operator and of a Matrix
media:group.media:description: Trace of an operator defined to be the sum of the eigenvalues (or of the eigenvalues of the complexification), repeated according to multiplicity. Trace of a matrix defined to be the sum of the squares of the diagonal enties. The connection between these two notions of trace.
